@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<section class="page-section">
    <div class="container px-4">
        <div class="policy-card reveal">
            <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p>At CarToGo, your privacy matters. This policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information while you use our service.</p>

            <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
            <p>We collect information you provide directly when you create an account or make a reservation, including your name, email address, phone number, and payment-related details. We also collect usage data and technical details about your visits to help improve the experience.</p>

            <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>To provide and manage your reservations.</li>
                <li>To communicate booking confirmations and updates.</li>
                <li>To improve our website, services, and support experience.</li>
                <li>To protect our platform and comply with legal obligations.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Cookies and Tracking</h2>
            <p>We use cookies and similar technologies to remember preferences, analyze traffic, and deliver a smoother browsing experience. You can manage cookies through your browser settings.</p>

            <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
            <p>We may share information with trusted partners who help us deliver the service, such as authentication providers and analytics platforms. We do not sell your personal data.</p>

            <h2>Security</h2>
            <p>We protect your data using industry-standard controls and encryption where appropriate. However, no online system is completely secure, so please use strong passwords and keep your account information safe.</p>

            <h2>Contact</h2>
            <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy or your information, please contact us through the support channels available on the site.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
